# AI Personal Assistant

## Description

This is a brief description of AI PA project.

## Features

- Language model chatbot
- Google search

## Installation

Here are the installation instructions for this project:

- Install python
- Install all required packages by running:
    sudo apt update && sudo apt install ffmpeg
    sudo apt install portaudio19-dev
    pip install -r requirements.txt
- Create .env file using .env.example as template
- Have fun

## Usage

Main point of this project is to make an AI chatbot with google search that uses voice recognition as an input.

